# Project Context — Colegio

School control platform: **parent monitoring** + **Moodle-style tasks**.

## Stack

| Layer | Tech |
|-------|------|
| Backend | Node.js + **NestJS** + TypeScript |
| Web | **Next.js 14** (App Router) + React + TypeScript |
| Mobile | **React Native** + Expo + TypeScript |
| DB | PostgreSQL 16 (see `specs/Database.md`) |
| API contract | `specs/Openapi.yml` — keep code in sync |

## Monorepo layout (planned)

```
apps/api/       NestJS
apps/web/       Next.js
apps/mobile/    React Native + Expo
packages/shared/     types, constants
packages/api-client/ generated from Openapi.yml
specs/          SDD source of truth (do not skip)
```

## Roles (RBAC)

`admin` | `director` | `teacher` | `student` | `parent`

- Admin/Director: **web only**
- Teacher/Student/Parent: **web + mobile**
- Parent: read-only on child data; cannot submit assignments

## SDD workflow

1. Change `specs/Userstories.md` (Gherkin) first when adding features
2. Update `Models.md`, `Database.md`, `Openapi.yml`
3. Implement + tests per `Testing.md` and `DefinitionOfDone.md`

## General rules

- TypeScript everywhere; no `any` without comment
- Spanish for user-facing strings; English for code identifiers
- Multi-tenant: always filter by `school_id` from JWT
- Minimize diff scope; match existing patterns in each app
